@startuml
title 受理闭环 / 可追踪化（DDD-Lite 组件图）

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

legend left
[M] 必须组件
[O] 可选组件（后续增强）
endlegend

actor "客户端/前端" as Client

package "Interfaces [M]" {
  component "DocumentIngestController [M]\nPOST /documents/upload\nGET /documents/{id}/status" as Controller
}

package "Application [M]" {
  component "AcceptUploadUseCase [M]" as AcceptUC
  component "GetDocumentStatusUseCase [M]" as StatusUC
}

package "Domain [M]" {
  component "Document 聚合 [M]\n(DocumentId, UploadStatus...)" as DocumentAgg
  component "DocumentRepository Port [M]" as RepoPort
  component "DocumentIdGenerator Port [M]" as IdPort
}

package "Infrastructure" {
  component "JdbcDocumentRepository [M]" as JdbcRepo
  component "UuidDocumentIdGenerator [M]" as UuidGen
  component "IngestWorker [O]" as Worker
  component "QueuePublisher [O]" as Publisher
}

database "PostgreSQL [M]\n(ingest_documents + vector tables)" as PG
queue "Message Queue [O]" as MQ
cloud "Embedding/LLM [O]" as LLM

Client --> Controller : HTTP 请求
Controller --> AcceptUC : 受理上传
Controller --> StatusUC : 查询状态

AcceptUC --> IdPort : 生成 DocumentId
AcceptUC --> RepoPort : save(Document:UPLOADED)
StatusUC --> RepoPort : findById(documentId)

RepoPort <|.. JdbcRepo
IdPort <|.. UuidGen

JdbcRepo --> PG : SQL 读写

AcceptUC ..> Publisher : 发布异步任务（可选）
Publisher ..> MQ : enqueue（可选）
MQ ..> Worker : consume（可选）
Worker ..> PG : 更新状态/写向量（可选）
Worker ..> LLM : Embedding/Chat（可选）

@enduml

